This is a missed-optimization in InstCombine.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i32 @not_d_allSignBits(i32 %cond, i32 %tval, i32 %fval) {
  %bitmask = ashr i32 %cond, 31
  %a1 = and i32 %tval, %bitmask
  %or = or i32 %bitmask, %fval
  %a2 = xor i32 %or, -1
  %sel = or i32 %a1, %a2
  ret i32 %sel
}

```

However, current LLVM cannot optimize the source program. The expected optimized program is
```llvm
define i32 @not_d_allSignBits(i32 %cond, i32 %tval, i32 %fval) {
  %1 = icmp slt i32 %cond, 0
  %2 = xor i32 %fval, -1
  %sel = select i1 %1, i32 %tval, i32 %2
  ret i32 %sel
}

```
